From 3afffe614ab8cca061eb424774fbbb278b785c17 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Salis Dev <dev@salis.app>
Date: Wed, 3 Jun 2026 10:30:31 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(storefront): fix pipe shuffle + hero flash + card
 animations
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

fixes:
- IntroLoader: track slots correctly → silaS rotates to Salis properly
- HeroSection: hide elements immediately via useEffect before GSAP loads
- page.tsx: wrap all content in opacity:0 div until introComplete

new animations (Phase 3):
- ProductCard: hover overlay with blur + CTA rises from bottom
- ProductCard: micro-interaction on add-to-cart (squeeze → bounce → ✓)
- ProductCard: image scale on hover
- ProductGrid: cards hidden by default, ScrollTrigger reveal with scale
- ScrollTrigger: once:true so animation runs once per session
